description:
Retailers that sell a variety of prosthetic devices and orthopedic
goods, and may or may not also conduct repair work. Products for
sale may include arch supports and other foot appliances, fracture
appliances, elastic hosiery, abdominal supporters, elastic and
orthopedic braces, canes, artificial limbs, wheel chairs, and walkers.
For merchants that primarily conduct repair work on orthopedic
goods, use MCC 7699.
